Backups and Log Rotation (Snapshot)

	* Manual (Starter Plan)

	* Automated (Only Pro Plan)

		-> Implemented in pro only
		-> Backup retention: It's need a support ticket to restore system backup.

			- Days 1-3 : One per hour
			- Days 4-7 : One per day
			- Weeks 2-6 : One per week
			- Weeks 8-12 : Every two weeks
			- Months 3-5 : One per month

		-> Log retention : (Archived once per day)

			- Default Name: /var/log/deploy.log
			- Archived Name: /var/log/deploy.log.10.gz
				-> 10 is equels to how many days passed since this log + 1
				-> Available for one year data.